\section*{streamit-2.0}

\begin{itemize}

\item Snapshot release of internal infrastructure (September 2006).
This snapshot has new features, bug fixes, and possibly new bugs
compared to the initial public release.  Major features are as
follows, please contact us if you have any questions:

\begin{itemize}
\item Multi-threaded backend for multicores and clusters of workstations.
\item Support for dynamic rates and teleport messaging.
\item Faster uniprocessor implementation (up to 2X).
\item Faster and more memory-efficient Java library (up to 10X).		      
\item MPEG-2 and JPEG applications (limited compiler support; full support in Java library).
\item Snapshot of cache optimizations and linear statespace analysis.
\end{itemize}

\item Initial public release (October 2003).
\end{itemize}

